      graduating in 2018. The math background shapes how I think about systems — I tend to look for patterns, optimize for
      efficiency, and think in abstractions.
    </p>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I build side projects (<a href="/projects/">see them here</a>), write about
      <a href="/writings/">things I'm learning</a>, and try to stay curious.
    </p>

